<i>[Episode 22]</i>

3
00:01:42,835 --> 00:01:44,755
Here comes the second glass of wine,

4
00:01:46,035 --> 00:01:49,835
It's for thanking you for rescuing Fuxian
and saving Song'er,

5
00:01:50,635 --> 00:01:52,035
Our Qu family

6
00:01:52,035 --> 00:01:55,075
could finally get rid of the shackles
of the Princess,

7
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,464
Song'er,

8
00:02:00,395 --> 00:02:02,835
you must make sure to express your gratitude

9
00:02:02,835 --> 00:02:05,015
to Senior Official Pei and Madam Kudi,

10
00:02:05,015 --> 00:02:07,635
They're our family's life savers,

11
00:02:10,144 --> 00:02:11,200
Song'er,

12
00:02:15,435 --> 00:02:18,195
Thank you, Senior Official Pei,
Thank you, Madam Kudi,

13
00:02:23,475 --> 00:02:24,608
You're too polite, young master,

14
00:02:30,395 --> 00:02:32,275
Chongyu, Lady Jing,

15
00:02:33,315 --> 00:02:36,915
You two should also thank Senior Official Pei
and his wife heartily,

16
00:02:38,755 --> 00:02:40,575
I've long considered Liuli as a sister,

17
00:02:40,575 --> 00:02:41,755
and saying thanks would be too formal,

18
00:02:42,355 --> 00:02:43,675
But I still want to thank you

19
00:02:44,235 --> 00:02:45,895
for risking your life

20
00:02:45,895 --> 00:02:47,715
for saving my sister-in-law and Song'er,

21
00:02:52,955 --> 00:02:54,016
Let's go,

22
00:02:55,115 --> 00:02:56,192
Sit here,

23
00:02:59,616 --> 00:03:00,704
Shouyue,

24
00:03:01,824 --> 00:03:02,848
thank you,

25
00:03:06,112 --> 00:03:07,200
Minister,

26
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,120
you're welcome,

27
00:03:20,115 --> 00:03:21,875
Protector-General, Minister,

28
00:03:22,995 --> 00:03:24,115
please forgive my rudeness,

29
00:03:24,995 --> 00:03:26,048
My wife and I

30
00:03:29,075 --> 00:03:31,355
would like to propose a toast to Prefect Wang,

31
00:03:41,472 --> 00:03:42,528
Prefect Wang,

32
00:03:43,635 --> 00:03:45,275
we're grateful for your assistance that night,

33
00:03:45,835 --> 00:03:47,235
If it wasn't for you,

34
00:03:47,235 --> 00:03:49,355
our dilemma in Xizhou
would not have been resolved,

35
00:03:49,915 --> 00:03:50,995
If it wasn't for you,

36
00:03:50,995 --> 00:03:52,995
we would not have been able to settle here,

37
00:03:54,355 --> 00:03:55,635
Prefect Wang,

38
00:03:55,635 --> 00:03:57,235
you are the benefactor of both me and Shouyue,

39
00:03:57,235 --> 00:03:58,475
I pay my respect to Prefect Wang,

40
00:04:05,952 --> 00:04:07,008
Junmeng,

41
00:04:08,195 --> 00:04:10,355
I treated you first as my brother-in-law,

42
00:04:10,355 --> 00:04:11,595
then as my brother,

43
00:04:13,115 --> 00:04:14,215
From this day forward,

44
00:04:14,215 --> 00:04:15,735
I'll see you as a brother first,

45
00:04:15,735 --> 00:04:16,915
then my brother-in-law,

46
00:04:20,475 --> 00:04:22,575
You saved my family,

47
00:04:22,575 --> 00:04:24,875
You saved my son,

48
00:04:24,875 --> 00:04:27,835
and you also saved
the Senior Official and his wife,

49
00:04:29,835 --> 00:04:31,315
You kept us a good official

50
00:04:31,315 --> 00:04:32,755
for our people in Xizhou,

51
00:04:32,755 --> 00:04:33,875
A toast for you

52
00:04:34,435 --> 00:04:37,275
along with the Senior Official's couple,

53
00:04:45,035 --> 00:04:46,112
Drink it up,

54
00:04:53,315 --> 00:04:54,395
Drink it up,

55
00:04:54,995 --> 00:04:56,515
So many people are toasting to you,

56
00:04:56,515 --> 00:04:57,595
and you're still pretending over there,

57
00:04:58,755 --> 00:04:59,955
Without you,

58
00:05:01,835 --> 00:05:03,195
I don't yet know when

59
00:05:03,195 --> 00:05:05,035
I'll be able to see my lovely grandson,

60
00:05:27,035 --> 00:05:28,035
Father-in-law,

61
00:05:29,888 --> 00:05:30,912
I toast to you,

62
00:05:31,635 --> 00:05:32,704
I,,,I'll drink it up,

63
00:05:33,595 --> 00:05:34,655
Good, good,

64
00:05:34,655 --> 00:05:35,744
Chongyu,

65
00:05:36,555 --> 00:05:39,155
Brother, I'll drink it up,

66
00:05:40,915 --> 00:05:43,075
Senior Official, Madam Kudi,

67
00:05:43,075 --> 00:05:45,115
I have caused a lot of offense in the past,
I'll drink it up,

68
00:05:49,035 --> 00:05:51,275
Aunt, I'll drink it up,

69
00:05:52,275 --> 00:05:53,875
Junmeng, don't drink too much,

70
00:05:56,435 --> 00:05:58,615
Young master, let's have a drink,

71
00:05:58,615 --> 00:05:59,648
Sit down for me,

72
00:06:05,995 --> 00:06:08,675
Come, let us all raise our cups together

73
00:06:09,515 --> 00:06:12,695
to thank the Senior Official Pei and his wife,

74
00:06:12,695 --> 00:06:13,795
Respect to the Senior Official's couple,

75
00:06:25,344 --> 00:06:30,784
<i>[Protector-General's Mansion]</i>

76
00:06:33,675 --> 00:06:34,915
Come, come, Make way, make way,

77
00:06:34,915 --> 00:06:37,475
Take a look at the trinket,

78
00:06:41,555 --> 00:06:43,235
Sanniang from An family requests an audience,
Master,

79
00:06:44,064 --> 00:06:45,184
Please let her in,

80
00:06:53,312 --> 00:06:54,336
Sister,

81
00:06:55,115 --> 00:06:56,995
There's no outsider in this room,
why the need for such formalities?

82
00:06:56,995 --> 00:06:58,080
Please come in,

83
00:07:04,515 --> 00:07:05,595
My visit this time is to

84
00:07:05,595 --> 00:07:07,075
report important matters to you,
Senior Official,

85
00:07:08,155 --> 00:07:09,555
Sister, thank you for

86
00:07:09,555 --> 00:07:10,835
having gathered so much grain and fodder,

87
00:07:11,755 --> 00:07:12,875
I can't conceal anything from you,

88
00:07:13,995 --> 00:07:15,395
From the past half month,

89
00:07:15,395 --> 00:07:17,795
many merchants and families have rushed here
from various counties and villages,

90
00:07:17,795 --> 00:07:19,515
which has indeed saved us
quite a bit of effort,

91
00:07:20,315 --> 00:07:21,895
The weather is quite good this year,

92
00:07:21,895 --> 00:07:23,995
The harvest in the counties of Xizhou
is also quite good,

93
00:07:23,995 --> 00:07:27,235
and I've heard good news
from places like Dunhuang and Qiuci,

94
00:07:27,235 --> 00:07:30,595
For now, we closed the deal
for 100,000 dan of grain,

95
00:07:30,595 --> 00:07:32,195
More than 50,000 dan have also been put
into the warehouse,

96
00:07:32,195 --> 00:07:33,475
The remaining 40,000 dan

97
00:07:33,475 --> 00:07:35,475
are estimated to be delivered continuously
by the end of the month,

98
00:07:35,475 --> 00:07:37,475
Most of the fodder has also been collected,

99
00:07:38,144 --> 00:07:39,232
That's great,

100
00:07:39,875 --> 00:07:42,675
It's just that
everyone's granaries are almost full,

101
00:07:43,195 --> 00:07:44,755
If more grains are sent here,

102
00:07:44,755 --> 00:07:45,835
I'm afraid we can't hold any more,

103
00:07:46,355 --> 00:07:48,195
I don't know
when we can start using the government granary,

104
00:07:48,915 --> 00:07:50,635
The granary will be opened for grain collection
in half a month,

105
00:07:51,315 --> 00:07:52,815
When the military warehouse collects grain,

106
00:07:52,815 --> 00:07:55,115
we pay half of the money to each business,

107
00:07:55,115 --> 00:07:56,315
The other half will be paid

108
00:07:56,315 --> 00:07:58,455
when they transport the grains
to the military warehouse,

109
00:07:58,455 --> 00:08:00,515
The payment can be redeemed with
the military warehouse's expense slips,

110
00:08:00,515 --> 00:08:01,795
What merchants fear the most

111
00:08:01,795 --> 00:08:03,475
is the accumulation of unpaid goods,

112
00:08:04,195 --> 00:08:06,995
Moreover,
purchasing such a large quantity of grain

113
00:08:06,995 --> 00:08:09,315
requires a lot of money,

114
00:08:09,875 --> 00:08:11,795
If one can truly

115
00:08:11,795 --> 00:08:13,815
receive half of the payment as agreed
after half a month,

116
00:08:13,815 --> 00:08:15,315
the pressure would be greatly reduced,

117
00:08:22,315 --> 00:08:24,395
Sister,
you're truly a person of meticulous thoughts,

118
00:08:25,355 --> 00:08:26,635
So many detailed matters

119
00:08:26,635 --> 00:08:27,995
have all been arranged neatly,

120
00:08:28,675 --> 00:08:29,995
It's all because of you,

121
00:08:29,995 --> 00:08:31,515
It's nothing,

122
00:08:31,515 --> 00:08:33,755
This was indeed a rare opportunity
not to be missed,

123
00:08:33,755 --> 00:08:36,315
Even our An family has a solid foundation
in Xizhou,

124
00:08:36,315 --> 00:08:37,835
but I have only been here twice,

125
00:08:38,515 --> 00:08:40,035
And this time

126
00:08:40,035 --> 00:08:41,515
almost all the wealthy merchants of Xizhou

127
00:08:41,515 --> 00:08:43,075
participated,

128
00:08:43,075 --> 00:08:44,375
Although there are difficulties

129
00:08:44,375 --> 00:08:46,015
this time,

130
00:08:46,015 --> 00:08:47,695
but as long as thing are carefully arranged,

131
00:08:47,695 --> 00:08:48,895
I believe

132
00:08:48,895 --> 00:08:51,155
the status of the An family
in the business world

133
00:08:51,155 --> 00:08:52,595
will rise with the tide,

134
00:08:56,955 --> 00:08:59,415
Master, Minister Qu invites you
to his residence,

135
00:08:59,415 --> 00:09:01,635
and he says it's about the Military Commander
of Congshan Route,

136
00:09:01,635 --> 00:09:03,775
General Su has sent a staff officer over,

137
00:09:03,775 --> 00:09:05,835
General Su's people sure arrived quickly,

138
00:09:06,515 --> 00:09:07,515
This General Su

139
00:09:08,515 --> 00:09:09,715
is not the one you think of,

140
00:09:21,515 --> 00:09:22,815
Senior Official Pei,

141
00:09:22,815 --> 00:09:24,195
you are late,

142
00:09:24,195 --> 00:09:25,355
You should be penalized,

143
00:09:26,304 --> 00:09:27,335
Protector-General,

144
00:09:27,335 --> 00:09:28,480
Minister,

145
00:09:31,995 --> 00:09:32,995
Shouyue,

146
00:09:32,995 --> 00:09:34,535
I didn't expect us to meet again

147
00:09:34,535 --> 00:09:35,755
this soon,

148
00:09:37,675 --> 00:09:38,915
It turns out to be Brother Ziyu,

149
00:09:38,915 --> 00:09:40,235
This is truly a pleasant surprise,

150
00:09:40,955 --> 00:09:43,475
You have followed General Su to Yizhou?

151
00:09:44,355 --> 00:09:46,235
<i>My father and I are now exiled to Yizhou,</i>

152
00:09:46,755 --> 00:09:48,395
<i>All thanks to you,</i>

153
00:09:51,104 --> 00:09:52,128
Exactly,

154
00:09:52,715 --> 00:09:54,195
I didn't expect the Emperor's grace
to be this immense,

155
00:09:54,195 --> 00:09:56,275
He granted me to serve
under my father's command,

156
00:09:56,795 --> 00:09:59,515
My father is now the Military Commander
of Congshan Route,

157
00:10:00,075 --> 00:10:01,115
I came here this time

158
00:10:01,115 --> 00:10:03,315
to supervise the military readiness in Xizhou,

159
00:10:04,315 --> 00:10:06,035
I'm afraid it may disturb your watch
for several days

160
00:10:07,955 --> 00:10:08,975
I couldn't ask for more,

161
00:10:08,975 --> 00:10:11,035
For the matter of supply and tax in Xizhou,

162
00:10:11,555 --> 00:10:12,835
just ask me,

163
00:10:12,835 --> 00:10:15,675
These matters are all entrusted to Shouyue,

164
00:10:15,675 --> 00:10:17,195
I am unaware of any,

165
00:10:17,195 --> 00:10:19,875
However, if you want to know
where to find the finest wine,

166
00:10:19,875 --> 00:10:22,115
or the most gorgeous performance,
then I'm your guy,

167
00:10:22,875 --> 00:10:23,995
You guys keep going,

168
00:10:26,795 --> 00:10:29,595
Just now, Chongyu mentioned he know nothing
about the money and grain,

169
00:10:30,235 --> 00:10:32,275
I thought it was just his modest talk,

170
00:10:33,635 --> 00:10:35,175
But I didn't expect that Pei Xingjian truly

171
00:10:35,175 --> 00:10:37,915
had the means to isolate the Qu's family,

172
00:10:39,936 --> 00:10:40,955
Shouyue,

173
00:10:41,835 --> 00:10:43,135
let's talk about official matters first

174
00:10:43,135 --> 00:10:44,335
before anything personal,

175
00:10:44,335 --> 00:10:45,715
Okay,

176
00:10:45,715 --> 00:10:47,475
I wonder how much supplies have been prepared
by Xizhou

177
00:10:47,475 --> 00:10:48,915
for the army,

178
00:10:48,915 --> 00:10:50,975
50,000 dan of millet and corn
have been prepared,

179
00:10:50,975 --> 00:10:52,975
along with 10,000 carts of forage and grain,

180
00:10:52,975 --> 00:10:54,455
Everything will be ready
by the end of the month,

181
00:10:54,455 --> 00:10:55,835
Once the army is here,

182
00:10:55,835 --> 00:10:57,555
we can immediately transport everything
to the military warehouse,

183
00:10:57,555 --> 00:10:59,475
Shouyue, you're not joking, right?

184
00:11:01,235 --> 00:11:03,155
The population of Xizhou is nearly 40,000,

185
00:11:03,155 --> 00:11:04,955
How can you only prepare 50,000 dan of corn?

186
00:11:05,835 --> 00:11:08,635
Yizhou's population is less than 10,000,
yet more than 20,000 dan have been prepared,

187
00:11:09,395 --> 00:11:11,595
The expedition of the army to the west
is a serious matter for our country,

188
00:11:11,595 --> 00:11:14,115
Do not joke about this;

189
00:11:14,115 --> 00:11:15,275
take it seriously
and do not treat it as child's play,

190
00:11:17,795 --> 00:11:19,755
Ziyu, there're things you don't know,

191
00:11:19,755 --> 00:11:21,975
Yizhou is a place where the land is vast,
and the population is sparse,

192
00:11:21,975 --> 00:11:23,475
Xizhou is

193
00:11:23,475 --> 00:11:24,515
Crowded but with less land,

194
00:11:25,435 --> 00:11:27,235
I have been struggling for the past two months,

195
00:11:27,755 --> 00:11:28,895
Buying grain at a high price,

196
00:11:28,895 --> 00:11:29,995
engaging traders,

197
00:11:30,515 --> 00:11:32,095
I have tried all kinds of methods,

198
00:11:32,095 --> 00:11:34,595
I was prepared for 100,000 dan
in the beginning,

199
00:11:35,355 --> 00:11:36,415
But now

200
00:11:36,415 --> 00:11:37,915
I could only be certain about 50,000 dan,

201
00:11:38,555 --> 00:11:40,715
If you add the rent from the summer harvest

202
00:11:41,395 --> 00:11:42,595
and the back-up supply in the granary,

203
00:11:43,115 --> 00:11:44,955
it's about 60,000 approximately,

204
00:11:47,035 --> 00:11:48,555
To be honest,

205
00:11:48,555 --> 00:11:50,955
I also know this is a difficult matter,

206
00:11:51,475 --> 00:11:53,475
But this time, the army has 100,000 people,

207
00:11:54,235 --> 00:11:57,375
Chief Administrator Cheng issued
a military order to my father a few days ago,

208
00:11:57,375 --> 00:11:58,955
Before the arrival of the army,

209
00:11:58,955 --> 00:12:00,755
the three states of Xi, Ting, and Yi must

210
00:12:00,755 --> 00:12:02,315
prepare the army rations
in the amount of three dan per household,

211
00:12:03,315 --> 00:12:04,315
If there're any violations,

212
00:12:04,835 --> 00:12:06,735
the military law will surely be discussed,

213
00:12:06,735 --> 00:12:07,995
Three dan per household,

214
00:12:12,915 --> 00:12:14,275
That's a total of 120,000 dan then,

215
00:12:15,315 --> 00:12:16,675
Don't worry too much, Shouyue,

216
00:12:17,435 --> 00:12:19,535
My father knows that you and I go way back,

217
00:12:19,535 --> 00:12:20,595
therefore,

218
00:12:20,595 --> 00:12:22,275
he specifically sent me to

219
00:12:22,275 --> 00:12:23,715
lend you a helping hand,

220
00:12:24,315 --> 00:12:25,635
I came with 300 elite solders this time

221
00:12:25,635 --> 00:12:27,875
by order,

222
00:12:28,555 --> 00:12:30,475
Once the grain is stored,
should there be a shortage,

223
00:12:31,035 --> 00:12:32,335
I will then dispatch my troops

224
00:12:32,335 --> 00:12:33,915
to levy grain from the villages,

225
00:12:33,915 --> 00:12:35,075
Master Su,

226
00:12:39,995 --> 00:12:42,075
I'll definitely do my best
to hand in the corns,

227
00:12:43,435 --> 00:12:44,675
But 120,000 dan

228
00:12:45,475 --> 00:12:47,755
have indeed exceeded the burden
of the people of Xizhou,

229
00:12:48,435 --> 00:12:50,575
You really have a kind heart,

230
00:12:50,575 --> 00:12:52,235
I respect that,

231
00:12:52,875 --> 00:12:54,455
However, the military orders are unyielding,

232
00:12:54,455 --> 00:12:56,435
there's no room for negotiation,

233
00:12:57,035 --> 00:12:58,595
You go ahead and collecting grain as you could,

234
00:12:59,195 --> 00:13:00,635
If it could be delivered in full,

235
00:13:00,635 --> 00:13:01,715
that's the best,

236
00:13:02,315 --> 00:13:04,455
If there's any shortage,

237
00:13:04,455 --> 00:13:06,155
I certainly will not sit by
and watch General Cheng

238
00:13:06,155 --> 00:13:07,915
have you subjected to the military law

239
00:13:07,915 --> 00:13:09,315
even if it means bearing a bad name,

240
00:13:11,115 --> 00:13:12,675
I have taken Ziyu's good intentions to heart,

241
00:13:13,435 --> 00:13:16,075
but could you grant me a few more days?

242
00:13:17,035 --> 00:13:18,615
The army is about to arrive,

243
00:13:18,615 --> 00:13:20,955
Even if I want to help you delay
for a few more days,

244
00:13:20,955 --> 00:13:22,315
but the military law is ruthless,

245
00:13:22,955 --> 00:13:25,915
You better not harbor any wishful thinking,

246
00:13:34,315 --> 00:13:36,555
Reporting to the Protector-General,
the plum juice is ready,

247
00:13:38,115 --> 00:13:39,395
Is it ready?

248
00:13:39,395 --> 00:13:40,435
Okay,

249
00:13:41,995 --> 00:13:45,835
Now that you two have done talking business,

250
00:13:45,835 --> 00:13:46,915
then let us

251
00:13:46,915 --> 00:13:48,355
go together and have a taste

252
00:13:48,355 --> 00:13:51,035
of plum juice from Meizhong County,

253
00:13:51,680 --> 00:13:52,704
Protector-General Qu,

254
00:13:53,315 --> 00:13:55,155
I will go and instruct the subordinates first

255
00:13:55,155 --> 00:13:56,435
to hurry up in collecting grains
from all places,

256
00:13:57,475 --> 00:14:00,115
Ziyu, I will take my leave first,

257
00:14:00,115 --> 00:14:01,595
When I have time,

258
00:14:01,595 --> 00:14:03,595
I will surely treat you to a good drink,

259
00:14:04,555 --> 00:14:07,015
You're indeed diligent in government affairs

260
00:14:07,015 --> 00:14:08,195
I am impressed,

261
00:14:19,675 --> 00:14:22,635
It seems that Senior Official Pei is too busy,

262
00:14:22,635 --> 00:14:24,115
Ziyu,

263
00:14:24,115 --> 00:14:25,555
